data.description: Beautiful two-story home in highly desirable Persimmon Grove community and in Lexington One school district. Spacious 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath with two of the bedrooms having private baths, perfect for guests or in law suite. Master bedroom has large walk-in closet, dual vanities, garden tub and separate shower. Large eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, gas stove and lots of cabinet and counter space. Fully private backyard with fish pond, irrigation well, screened porch and storage building. Community pool within walking distance and includes clubhouse, children's playground, community pond, gazebo and walking trails with sidewalks throughout. Close proximity to I-20 and easy access to downtown Columbia or Lexington. Call me today to schedule a private showing!
